<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'About Us — Pixel Wave Logistics' }) %>
<%- include('partials/header', { active: 'about' }) %>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">OUR STORY</div>
  <h1>Built for visibility.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Pixel Wave Logistics started with a simple frustration: shipping updates that told you nothing. No location, no timestamp, no real status — just "in transit" for days on end. We built a network where every shipment reports back in real time, at every step.</p>
  <div class="signal-track"></div>
</div>

<div class="stats-row" style="margin-bottom:60px;">
  <div class="stat" style="background:transparent;border-color:var(--line);"><b style="color:var(--amber);">120+</b><span>Countries served</span></div>
  <div class="stat" style="background:transparent;border-color:var(--line);"><b style="color:var(--amber);">24/7</b><span>Live tracking</span></div>
  <div class="stat" style="background:transparent;border-color:var(--line);"><b style="color:var(--amber);">3</b><span>Service tiers</span></div>
</div>

<div class="section-title">What we believe.</div>
<p class="section-sub">A few principles that shape how we build and operate.</p>

<div class="service-grid">
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="icon-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 3"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Real-time, always</h3>
    <p>A status update isn't real unless it has a location and a timestamp attached to it. We don't ship vague.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="icon-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 3l8 4v5c0 5-3.5 8-8 9-4.5-1-8-4-8-9V7l8-4z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>No black boxes</h3>
    <p>Customers shouldn't have to call anyone to find out where their freight is. The tracking page is the source of truth.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="icon-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 12h16M4 6h16M4 18h10"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Small team, wide reach</h3>
    <p>We stay lean on purpose — fewer handoffs means fewer places for a shipment to go quiet.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card" style="padding:24px;margin-bottom:60px;">
  <p class="lede" style="margin:0;">Questions about how we operate, or interested in working together? <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--amber);text-decoration:underline;">Get in touch</a> — we read every message.</p>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
